    <div class="card-content">
      <p><em>Transcript excerpt:</em></p>
      <div class="glitch-line">VOICE (unknown, cracked line): "<span>...why haven’t you burned it yet?</span>"</div>
      <div class="glitch-line">"[click] The letter was never for her. She just—she wouldn’t stop copying it down."</div>
      <div class="glitch-line">"She thought she was safe once it was in Latin."</div>
      <div class="glitch-line"><span>"You weren’t meant to hear this. You weren’t meant to read it."</span></div>
      <div class="glitch-line">"Shafiq warned her—<span class='arabic'>شفيق العيد</span>—but she was already writing."</div>
      <div class="glitch-line">"[distortion—pause]"</div>
      <div class="glitch-line">"...No, I never saw his face."</div>
      <div class="glitch-line">"...But he remembered mine."</div>
      <p><em>Transcript fragment ends. No carrier signal detected after timestamp 00:36:12.</em></p>
    </div>

    <div class="card-notes">
